<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Techy Software</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
    }
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e54c8, #8f94fb);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    nav {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e54c8, #8f94fb);
      padding: 10px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    nav ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    nav ul li {
      display: inline;
      margin-right: 20px;
    }
    nav ul li a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    section {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    footer {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4e54c8, #8f94fb);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .portfolio-images {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .portfolio-images img {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 10px;
    }
    .feedback-form {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .feedback-form input[type="text"],
    .feedback-form input[type="email"],
    .feedback-form textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 10px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .feedback-form input[type="submit"] {
      background-color: #4e54c8;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Welcome to Techy Software</h1>
  </header>
  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Products</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Services</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
  <section>
    <h2>About Techy Software</h2>
    <p>Techy Software is a leading software development company specializing in innovative solutions for businesses of all sizes.</p>
    <h2>Our Products</h2>
    <p>Explore our wide range of software products designed to streamline your operations and boost productivity.</p>
    <h2>Our Services</h2>
    <p>We offer a variety of services including custom software development, web application development, and mobile app development.</p>
  </section>
  <footer>
    <h2>Feedback Form</h2>
    <form action="/feedback" method="POST">
      <label for="name">Name:</label><br>
      <input type="text" id="name" name="name"><br>
      <label for="email">Email:</label><br>
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email"><br>
      <label for="feedback">Feedback:</label><br>
      <textarea id="feedback" name="feedback"></textarea><br>
      <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    </form>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
